column2: SELECT s.z             , ROUND((petroR5#_g + petroR5#_r + petroR5#_i) / # , #) AS AVGpetroR5#_gri             , ROUND((petroRad_g + petroRad_r + petroRad_i) / # / # , #) AS AVGpetroRad_griDIV2.#             , ROUND( (AVG(petroR5#Err_g/petroR5#_g) + AVG(petroR5#Err_r/petroR5#_r) + AVG(petroR5#Err_i/petroR5#_i)) / # * #, #) AS AVGR5#ErrorPct             , ROUND(AVG(s.zErr/s.z * #), #) AS AVGzErrPct             FROM mydb.MyTable             AND petroR5#_g BETWEEN # AND #             AND petroR5#Err_g >= #             AND petroR5#_r BETWEEN # AND #             AND petroR5#Err_r >= #             AND petroR5#_i BETWEEN # AND #             AND petroR5#Err_i >= #             AND petroR5#Err_g / petroR5#_g < #             AND petroR5#Err_r / petroR5#_r < #             AND petroR5#Err_i / petroR5#_i < #
